text: Commando is a 1985 American action movie directed by Mark L. Lester and starring Arnold Schwarzenegger, Rae Dawn Chong, Alyssa Milano, Vernon Wells, Bill Duke and Dan Hedaya. The movie was released in the United States on October 4, 1985. == Cast == * Arnold Schwarzenegger as Colonel John Matrix * Rae Dawn Chong as Cindy * Dan Hedaya as Arius * Vernon Wells as Bennett * James Olson as General Franklin Kirby * David Patrick Kelly as Sully * Alyssa Milano as Jenny Matrix * Bill Duke as Cooke ==Other websites== * Category:1985 action movies Category:1980s American action movies Category:1980s English- language movies Category:Movies about terrorism Category:Movies about abduction Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Mark L. Lester Category:Movies set in South America
